com.seagullsw.appinterface.client

Interface ClientFunctionDataConverter

  • All Superinterfaces:
    com.seagullsw.appinterface.model.data.ValueConverter
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ClientFunctionDataConverterAdapter

    public interface ClientFunctionDataConverter
extends com.seagullsw.appinterface.model.data.ValueConverter

    Defines methods for converting the data values in Request objects from Java objects to an external representation (such as Strings), and in Response objects from such an external representation back to Java objects.

    NOTE: This interface is not intended for general use by clients. Its public access privilege is an implementation artifact.
